title: Malwarebytes Anti-Malware v2.1.8.1057 + Serial
description: Malwarebytes Anti-Malware Premium is the latest version of The Anti-Malware Formerly Known As Malwarebytes Anti-Malware Pro. Malwarebytes Anti-Malware (MBAM) 2.0 ships with a completely redesigned user interface to make the product easier to use, more informative and provide quicker access to key functionality. MBAM 2.0 also built in and improved our Anti-Rootkit and Chameleon self-protection technologies. Most importantly, MBAM 2.0's detection and removal engine are significantly improved under the hood. Malwarebytes Anti-Malware Premium's industry-leading scanner detects and removes malware like worms, Trojans, rootkits, rogues, spyware, and more. All you have to do is launch Malwarebytes Anti-Malware Premium and run a scan. It's that simple. It provides better protection and its instant real-time scanner that automatically prevents malware and websites from infecting your PC. Either way you're crushing malware and foiling hackers
